Photos.Controller

Class SearchController

  • java.lang.Object
    • Photos.Controller.Controller
      • Photos.Controller.PhotoController
        • Photos.Controller.SearchController

  • public class SearchController
extends PhotoController
    Handles the Search action of the user. Can search for photos in all albums based on date or tags. All searches must be inputted correctly.
    Author:
    Krysti Leong, April Dizon
